## ANIMATION SYSTEM
Dùng DOTween (khuyên dùng) hoặc Unity Coroutine + AnimationCurve

### A. Start Play — Chia bài
```
for each row (top → bottom):
  for each card in row (left → right):
    card.position = DealOrigin (góc phải màn hình, stack)
    card.rotation = Random(-15, 15)
    card.DOMove(targetPos, 0.25f).SetDelay(rowIdx*0.15f + colIdx*0.06f)
         .SetEase(Ease.OutBack)
    card.DORotate(0, 0.2f)
    // Lật:
    card.DOScaleX(0, 0.12f).OnComplete(() => {
        SetFrontSprite();
        card.DOScaleX(1, 0.12f).SetEase(Ease.OutBack);
    })
```

### B. Nhấc card (OnPointerDown)
```
card.DOScale(1.15f, 0.12f).SetEase(Ease.OutBack)
card.DORotate(5f * inputDirection, 0.1f)   // nghiêng theo hướng kéo
SortingOrder = topLayer
GhostCard.SetActive(true)      // back card tại vị trí gốc
HapticManager.Light()
AudioManager.PlaySFX("pick_up")
```

### C. Đang kéo (OnDrag)
```
float wobble = Mathf.Sin(Time.time * 12f) * 3f * dragSpeed
card.transform.rotation = Quaternion.Euler(0, 0, wobble)
card.transform.position = pointerWorld + offset
```

### D. Thả ra — Không có target
```
GhostCard.SetActive(false)
card.DOMove(originalPos, 0.25f).SetEase(Ease.OutBack)
card.DOScale(1.0f, 0.15f)
card.DORotate(0, 0.15f)
HapticManager.Soft()
AudioManager.PlaySFX("drop_fail")
```

### E. Thả ra — Có target (swap)
```
GhostCard.SetActive(false)
card.DOMove(targetCard.pos, 0.2f).SetEase(Ease.InOutQuad)
targetCard.DOMove(card.originalPos, 0.2f).SetEase(Ease.InOutQuad)
card.DOScale(1.0f, 0.15f)
HapticManager.Medium()
AudioManager.PlaySFX("drop_success")
// Sau khi swap xong → check done
```

### F. Row Done Sequence
```
Step 1 (0.0s): 4 card background flash → accentColor (DOColor, 0.1s)
Step 2 (0.1s): Scale stagger trái→phải
  card[0].DOScale(1.25f, 0.12f).SetDelay(0.00f)
  card[1].DOScale(1.25f, 0.12f).SetDelay(0.06f)
  card[2].DOScale(1.25f, 0.12f).SetDelay(0.12f)
  card[3].DOScale(1.25f, 0.12f).SetDelay(0.18f)
Step 3 (0.45s): Tất cả về 1.0f cùng lúc
Step 4 (0.6s): Row bay lên "done tray" (top area)
  row.DOMove(doneTrayPos, 0.35f).SetEase(Ease.InBack)
  row.DOFade(0, 0.3f).SetDelay(0.05f)
Step 5 (0.65s): Các hàng còn lại DOMove shift up
HapticManager.Success()
AudioManager.PlaySFX("row_done")
ParticleManager.Burst(rowCenter, starBurst)
```

### G. Spawn từ Pool
```
Step 1: 4 ô trống animate gom về phải (DOMove, 0.2s)
Step 2: Lật úp từ phải → trái (DOScaleX 0→1 với back sprite)
Step 3: Rải bài về vị trí từ trái → phải (DOMove + flip to front)
AudioManager.PlaySFX("deal")
```

### H. Card Highlight (hover/adjacent hint)
Khi kéo card qua ô trống hoặc card khác trong cùng hàng:
```
targetCard.DOScale(1.08f, 0.1f)  // nhấp nhô nhẹ
targetCard.borderGlow.DOFade(0.6f, 0.1f)
```

## HAPTIC MANAGER
Dùng Lofelt/Nice Vibrations hoặc Handheld.Vibrate() fallback

```csharp
public enum HapticType { Light, Soft, Medium, Heavy, Success, Warning, Error }

public class HapticManager : Singleton {
    public bool IsEnabled = true;
    public void Play(HapticType type) {
        if (!IsEnabled) return;
        switch(type) {
            case HapticType.Light:   /* selection changed */ break;
            case HapticType.Soft:    /* card dropped/fail */ break;
            case HapticType.Medium:  /* swap success */      break;
            case HapticType.Heavy:   /* error */             break;
            case HapticType.Success: /* row done */          break;
        }
    }
}
```

### Mapping rung theo event
