## RESPONSIVE BOARD
CardSize tính động:
```csharp
float cardWidth = (screenWidth - padding * 2) / 4f;
float cardHeight = cardWidth * 1.4f;   // aspect ratio bài
float boardHeight = cardHeight * activeRowCount + rowGap * (activeRowCount-1);
// Nếu boardHeight > safeAreaHeight → scale down toàn board
float scale = Mathf.Min(1f, safeAreaHeight / boardHeight);
boardContainer.localScale = Vector3.one * scale;
```

